SELECT 
                    script_path, 
                    is_flow, 
                    workspace_id, 
                    active_mode,
                    edited_by, 
                    email, 
                    path, 
                    error_handler_path as "error_handler_path: _", 
                    error_handler_args as "error_handler_args: _", 
                    retry as "retry: _" 
                FROM email_trigger 
                WHERE local_part = $1 
                    AND workspaced_local_part = FALSE

SELECT 
                    script_path, 
                    is_flow, 
                    workspace_id, 
                    edited_by, 
                    email, 
                    path, 
                    error_handler_path as "error_handler_path: _", 
                    error_handler_args as "error_handler_args: _", 
                    retry as "retry: _" 
                FROM email_trigger 
                WHERE local_part = $1 
                    AND workspaced_local_part = FALSE
                    AND enabled IS TRUE
